{"tid":2200349,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Ubisoft 免費推出 VR.巴黎聖母院","createTime":"2020-09-13T01:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T06:15:21.000Z","uid":33359,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b78562f3895ee2fe2b22e0079fa97298ee6684","tid":2200349,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"作者: ZMTL ([詠冬]瀟湘滅光) 看板: VR<br />\n標題: [情報] Ubisoft 免費推出 VR.巴黎聖母院<br />\n時間: Sat Sep 12 15:10:36 2020<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=203077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D203077&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513bVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=be4c1736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=203077</a><br />\nUbisoft 今日免費推出《巴黎聖母院：時光倒流之旅》 讓世人重溫經典建築風貌<br />\n（GNN 記者 RU 報導） 2020-09-11 15:15:58<br />\n<br />\n本文:<br />\n  Ubisoft 今（11）日於 Ubisoft Forward 線上發表會宣布，今日起在 Steam 平台免<br />\n費推出 VR 導覽遊戲《巴黎聖母院：時光倒流之旅（暫譯，Notre-Dame de Paris:<br />\nJourney Back in Time）》，帶領玩家以虛擬實境方式來感受巴黎聖母院大教堂輝煌風貌<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/51/659a341b727906087fb5af2ef519ufb5.JPG?w=1000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F51%2F659a341b727906087fb5af2ef519ufb5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513bVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=71ca1b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/51/659a341b727906087fb5af2ef519ufb5.JPG?w=1000</a><br />\n<br />\n  2019 年 4 月 15 日巴黎聖母院大教堂慘遭兇猛火舌吞噬而幾近全毀，令世人感到震<br />\n驚，而大教堂目前因重建整修而封閉。Ubisoft 希望藉由提供《巴黎聖母院：時光倒流之<br />\n旅》 VR 體驗，讓世人現今有機會透過虛擬實境來造訪這座大教堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfY86nYVki0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfY86nYVki0&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513bVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=cef93dca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfY86nYVki0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  Ubisoft 表示，《巴黎聖母院：時光倒流之旅》是運用 2014 年發行的遊戲《刺客教<br />\n條：大革命》的核心本質，結合 3D 技術重現巴黎聖母院，這項大工程的背後是歷時<br />\n 5000 個小時精雕細琢的繪圖作業，並在史學家指導之下而完成。<br />\n<br />\n  Ubisoft 指出，這趟虛擬之旅提供多種視角，帶領玩家觀看原本大教堂的歷史風貌，<br />\n而當中部分視角是一般大眾過去無法體驗的，旅程最後以乘坐熱氣球飛躍拱門畫下句點，<br />\n呈現活靈活現的十八世紀巴黎氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/54/631078466c51293913f4bc578519ufe5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F54%2F631078466c51293913f4bc578519ufe5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=bb1ee643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/55/3f925e3351b74caae9cc547da619uff5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F55%2F3f925e3351b74caae9cc547da619uff5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=3503e3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  研發團隊希望玩家可以進入遊戲中四處看看、並踏出幾步去欣賞這座歷史遺跡的各個<br />\n面向、細細聆聽名卡瓦葉-科爾管風琴演奏 J.S. Bach 樂曲的悠揚樂音。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/53/0ab8c9374cac2d81331e278ffb19ufd5.JPG?w=500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F53%2F0ab8c9374cac2d81331e278ffb19ufd5.JPG%3Fw%3D500&h=dba87b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/52/80df5200cf947fa5b75a61638019ufc5.JPG?w=500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F52%2F80df5200cf947fa5b75a61638019ufc5.JPG%3Fw%3D500&h=4d335843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  《巴黎聖母院：時光倒流之旅》是於去年歐洲文化遺產日在聯合國教科文組織總部首<br />\n度呈現，也曾入選美國知名藝術節 South by Southwest Virtual Cinema 2020，如今正<br />\n式在 Steam 平台免費推出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1341280/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1341280%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513bVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=4469b01a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1341280/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1599894953.A.697.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FSteam%2FM.1599894953.A.697.html&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513bVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=29c2b2da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Steam/M.1599894953.A.697.html</a><br />\n<br />\nUBI世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb90f7c3a8a3a48ac9b9b81679702a1e991e181","tid":2200349,"uid":189911,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會有好多bugs"},{"pid":"b68e5209aa8276bb891920f672480f1a63d2d36b","tid":2200349,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb90f7c3a8a3a48ac9b9b81679702a1e991e181","tid":2200349,"uid":189911,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會有好多bugs"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd34fc4cb43949e44646f35e6571389c8a7b8b1c","tid":2200349,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b68e5209aa8276bb891920f672480f1a63d2d36b","tid":2200349,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb90f7c3a8a3a48ac9b9b81679702a1e991e181","tid":2200349,"uid":189911,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:25:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會有好多bugs"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"可能到時候會卡住咗喺個聖母像入面"},{"pid":"8c964972ed7d5d2156b2f981fa0be8218668338f","tid":2200349,"uid":20222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"Ubi 長期整依d 好過啦唔好整game 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7797db8011d650eb28ef4469085a9ce89632286","tid":2200349,"uid":18220,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-1